sualize execution traces linking noun phrases to detected objects and relational reasoning steps. Baselines include SCAN, UNIALIGN, and TreeLSTM-based models. We expect NSR to achieve superior performance in all metrics, especially in compositional splits, demonstrating the benefit of syntax as an active computational mechanism rather than a passive constraint.",
